{"about_the_game":"Don't lose your emotions over this adorable 3D platformer! Play as a little pigeon, herd up your feelings, get your sheep together!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683710/extras/bannersheep.gif?t=1664180493\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock your hidden potential through our (totally legitimate image-based) mood matrix<br></li><li>Jump, shrink and dash your way through perilous platformer challenges<br></li><li>Herd up Happy, Angry and Sad sheep into the Orb of Emotional Importance<br></li><li>Don't hold in too many feelings or face explosive results!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683710/extras/bannersheepabout.gif?t=1664180493\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">You are a pigeon with a lot of pent-up feelings!</h2>With your powers, collect the fluffy remains of your emotions and bottle them up safely in the Orb of Emotional Importance.<br><br><br>Help fill out our mood matrix which determines your starting abilities<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683710/extras/charaselect.gif?t=1664180493\" /><br><br>Use your emotional abilities against the moody obstacle courses, collect sheep and keep your cool!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683710/extras/3powers.gif?t=1664180493\" /><br><br>Collect sheep of various colours and emotions and transfer your collected sheep into the Orb at the end of each course to prevent an emotional overload<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683710/extras/birdlook.gif?t=1664180493\" /><br><br>Watch how many sheeps you collect or you may be overwhelmed by your own emotions and blow up!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683710/extras/explode.gif?t=1664180493\" /><br><br><i><strong>DISCLAIMER:</strong> No sheep were harmed in the making of this video game</i>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"A pigeon is you!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1683710/5d9a93caef68eb7eed98becb98a1f6e83d17fe22.jpg"},{"name":"Getting over it","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1683710/f3c0ecdda43bc50c03dda1917ffd62c819fd0e9f.jpg"},{"name":"Bottled Emotions","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1683710/079d3f2db318b5f1f356fd0db104c028e987719d.jpg"},{"name":"Counting Sheep","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1683710/1abf7ea643ab83be8712ff73adfba6f26216a83a.jpg"},{"name":"Champion of Emotions","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1683710/34095d3dd3118ea10e869a3f6a2f2323eece64a0.jpg"},{"name":"Anger Management","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1683710/2e394f014de1e18d3a2be4fc23b076616d77f044.jpg"},{"name":"No More Tears","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1683710/64a2af6a10c0a49c85f5e968acd98135bb7724fc.jpg"},{"name":"The Little Things in Life","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1683710/f2f23c3f83ddc68014e9c32e7cc7eb8379ff93c1.jpg"},{"name":"CAMPBONK","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1683710/c16bc0c0bbbfc6c414bdc9e4552d5ecccaa7ce8c.jpg"},{"name":"Bird's the word","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1683710/1d4ee8850887fcd8a797c7864797175768e068ee.jpg"}],"total":16},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683710/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1664180493","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683710/page.bg.